defaultMessage: By submitting this offer/request, you allow us to send you email updates about matched drivers/passengers, and to create Whatsapp groups matching you to drivers/passengers.
You also acknowledge and have read our terms and conditions as found {link}
You will be shown other voters who are travelling the same way as you, and vice-versa. They will be able to request your contact information.
It is an offence to induce someone to vote for a political party. We only provide carpool-matching to connect voters - if anyone tries to induce you to vote for any party, please report this to us.
